Huge unnecessary nitpick: you could add trailing commas in your query statements, like this:
```
data: {
   ...
   body_part: input.body_part,
   category: input.category,
   workoutId: input.workoutId, <--- note this comma here even though the list ends here
}
```

This will prevent Github from saying that this line was modified if we need to add stuff to this list.
